{"type":"message","id":"c83df16e","parentId":"4c1b8460","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:41:23.745Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-30 09:41:20 GMT-3] Gateway restart update error (npm)\nSystem: Reason: global update (omit optional)\nSystem: Run: openclaw doctor --non-interactive\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/User-OEM/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 09:41 (America/Sao_Paulo) / 2026-03-30 12:41 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774874483681}}
